---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume | Robert Dudley" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5 text-justify">
    With over 12 years of expertise in UX, I have mastered an array of tools and
    methodologies to deliver superior user experiences. I'm at my best in
    environments where technology and users intersect. In my journey, I've
    created a framework for UX practices, implementing comprehensive design
    systems, and instilling key user testing and design principles in our
    research and design team. I further built upon this foundation through
    uncovering business needs and mapping them to our product outcomes that
    address requirements of designers, engineers, and other stakeholders.
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Staff, UX Designer, Walmart Global Tech"
      subtitle="Nov 2023 - present"
    >
      <p class="my-2 text-justify">
        Specializing in user discovery, managing functional partnerships, and
        design standards to drive customer-centric solutions, I support our
        design team through establishing consistency in our working process,
        delivering data-driven design through analytics, and influencing
        stakeholder consensus.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc md:columns-1 columns-1 mx-6 mb-5">
        <li>
          Developed our design team standards to support the Associate Digital
          Experience.
        </li>
        <li>
          Collaborated with stakeholders to establish KPIs for workflow
          efficiency, task management, and team collaboration.
        </li>
        <li>Conducted design reviews to ensure consistency and usability.</li>
        <li>
          Established user-focused analytics goals through collaboration with
          Product, Design, and Engineering stakeholders.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="UX Architecture Manager, BeyondTrust"
      subtitle="January 2022 to September 2023 - Remote"
    >
      <p class="my-2 text-justify">
        This team was the foundation to developing and maintaining the
        BeyondTrust design system to increase developer throughput, ensure
        design consistency across product areas, and centralize communication
        between all stakeholders for design.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc md:columns-1 columns-1 mx-6 mb-5">
        <li>
          Led a team of UX Engineers, Information Architects, and UX Writers to
          design, develop, and deliver an in-house Design System for all
          BeyondTrust products.
        </li>
        <li>
          Supported the UX team’s coded prototype efforts to decrease delivery
          time by 33%.
        </li>
        <li>
          Collaborated with Product Managers, Product Owners, and other
          Engineering leaders to plan and prioritize implementation of Design
          System standards.
        </li>
        <li>
          Coach and mentor UX Designers on usability best practices while
          working toward solving user challenges.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>

    <TimeLineElement
      title="Lead UX Prototyper, BeyondTrust"
      subtitle="March 2021 to January 2022 - Remote"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc md:columns-1 columns-1 mx-6 mb-5">
        <li>Increased user satisfaction by 19% through testing prototypes.</li>
        <li>
          Created a component library for rapid delivery of prototypes for user
          testing.
        </li>
        <li>
          Delivered accessibility enhancements based on feedback from VPAT
          analysis.
        </li>
        <li>Lead team of UI engineers to support research and design.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>

    <TimeLineElement
      title="Senior UX Researcher, BeyondTrust"
      subtitle="April 2020 to March 2021 - Remote"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc md:columns-1 columns-1 mx-6 mb-5">
        <li>
          Conducted heuristic evaluations and qualitative studies of
          BeyondTrust’s Password Safe product.
        </li>
        <li>
          Assessed current state user flows and interfaces through customer
          interviews.
        </li>
