        <li>
          Kickstarted the UX practice within Dillard’s IT as a team of 1,
          growing to 8 in the span of 5 years.
        </li>
        <li>
          Designed and implemented user experiences and accessibility best
          practices for Dillard’s enterprise applications and eCommerce.
        </li>
        <li>
          Established a front-end framework to unify the user experience across
          enterprise applications.
        </li>
        <li>
          Conducted qualitative and quantitative studies with enterprise users
          to uncover pain points and inefficiencies.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h4><b>Top Projects</b></h4>
      <ul class="list-disc md:columns-1 columns-1 mx-6 mb-5">
        <li>
          <b>Risk Management:</b> Developed system to manage incidents across Dillard's
          300+ locations.
        </li>
        <li>
          <b>Product Attribution (MDM solution):</b> Designed and tested product
          attribution process to support 100+ users and over 1,000,000 products for
          improved forecasting and analysis.
        </li>
        <li>
          <b>Dillards.com (eCommerce):</b> Ground-up responsive redesign of the eCommerce
          site with a focus on accessibility enhancements.
        </li>
        <li>
          <b>Enterprise Image Management:</b> Conducted contextual inquiries with
          users in all phases of the image process. Created designs to track the
          touchpoints from image creation to publishing on dillards.com.
        </li>
